        <p class="templatemo-light-gray-text"> Our initiative is to help the people who are in crisis of the resources and to motivate the people to donate resources which can be reused like books, clothes and also to motivate people to volunteer themselves in the events like blood donation, sanitation programs, event management etc. </p>
        <ul class="templatemo-light-gray-text templatemo-about-list">
          <li>Platform</li>
          <li>Sustainability</li>
          <li>Reuse of resource</li>
          <li>Reward points</li>
          <li>Help each other</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-7 col-sm-7 templatemo-about-right">
